"""
PART III Income

15. Income for the purposes of the Act

(4)

Editorial note: current text valid from 2025-03-21.

The adjustments specified in this paragraph are those made in accordance with—

(c)

section 30DD or section 30E of the 1992 Act (reductions in incapacity benefit in respect of pensions and councillor’s allowances).
"""

adjustment_made_in_accordance_with_section_30dd_of_1992_act:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean

adjustment_made_in_accordance_with_section_30e_of_1992_act:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean

adjustment_made_in_accordance_with_section_30dd_or_section_30e_15_4_c:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean
    from 2025-03-21:
        adjustment_made_in_accordance_with_section_30dd_of_1992_act or adjustment_made_in_accordance_with_section_30e_of_1992_act
